ment/lizzo-on-body-positive-movement-distortion">Lizzo</a>, who recently revealed a new psychedelic mani (courtesy of her nail artist <a class href="https://www.bustle.com/style/lizzo-bbmas-vote-dress-nails">Eri Ishizu</a>) on her Instagram story, they can also be <a class href="https://www.bustle.com/style/90s-inspired-nail-art-designs-manicure">colorful </a>and â60s-inspired. Of course, daisies can also be dotted along on an otherwise <a class href="https://www.bustle.com/p/the-5-best-clear-nail-polishes-22868862">clear nail</a> for a more classic and minimalist look, as was the case for Bieberâs nails (just one of the modelâs <a class href="https://www.bustle.com/style/hailey-bieber-nail-art-colorful-french-manicure">many impressive manicures</a>). </p><p>Fortunately, daisy nails are also <em>super</em> easy and <a class href="https://www.bustle.com/p/how-to-do-at-home-manicure-according-to-nail-experts-22631144">DIY-friendly</a>. The best part? You probably already have all the tools youâll need on-hand. âTo achieve a daisy look, you'll need a bobby pin, white polish, and yellow polish,â Bieberâs go-to <a class href="https://www.thewallgroup.com/artist/kimmie-kyees" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">nail artist </a><a class href="https://www.instagram.com/kimmiekyees/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Kimmie Kyees</a> tells Bustle over email. Read on for Kyeesâ simple, three-step guide to nailing (sorry, had to) summerâs cheeriest beauty trend.</p><div class="sCC iGR CkP"><figure class="QMg EJM"><div style="padding-top: 179.5518%;" class="vxZ CkP apK"><noscript><img src="https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/55b69b8d-36da-4c58-8b0d-bee41b4d8500-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-95213-am.png?w=414&amp;h=743&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=focalpoint&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fp-x=0.62&amp;fp-y=0.7867756315007429" srcSet="https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/55b69b8d-36da-4c58-8b0d-bee41b4d8500-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-95213-am.png?w=41