 thatâs as fully pigmented and opaque as possible.</p><div class="sCC iGR DDo"><div class="eFL bwf"><div class="SEh OHp"><div class="sCC Ffs vEZ"><div class><div class="iDB"><a class="Rya LAc" data-skimlink target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://orlybeauty.com/products/white-tips?variant=12954428571747&amp;currency=USD&amp;utm_medium=product_sync&amp;utm_source=google&amp;utm_content=sag_organic&amp;utm_campaign=sag_organic&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwwqaGBhBKEiwAMk-FtL6rC8Xx4J8grkXFLyVCXMnE0MjXiKoqz9Z5BqxOtFPMUXJvs7yIUhoCLwMQAvD_BwE"><div class="MQL Nut"><div class="yPq csi">Breathable Nail Polish In White Tips</div><div class="OQa chk">Orly</div></div><div class="ozJ qnK"><div class="vxZ wx_ IVX"><noscript><img src="https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/40c65b63-e1c7-4062-9d84-1ca063c1f6f4-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-13009-pm.png?w=400&amp;h=387&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress" srcSet="https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/40c65b63-e1c7-4062-9d84-1ca063c1f6f4-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-13009-pm.png?w=330&amp;h=319&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress 330w, https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/40c65b63-e1c7-4062-9d84-1ca063c1f6f4-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-13009-pm.png?w=330&amp;h=319&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;q=50&amp;dpr=2 660w, https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/40c65b63-e1c7-4062-9d84-1ca063c1f6f4-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-13009-pm.png?w=400&amp;h=387&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress 400w, https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/40c65b63-e1c7-4062-9d84-1ca063c1f6f4-screen-shot-2021-06-16-at-13009-pm.png?w=400&amp;h=387&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;q=50&amp;dpr=2 800w" sizes="(min-width:768px) 400px, 330px" alt="Breathable Nail Polish In White Tips" class="Eds" /></noscript></div></div><button class="yhy kYY"><span class="otN Owp"><span class="RdH">$9.99</span></span></button><button cl