Fr"></div></div></div></div><p></p><h2>3. Add The Center Of The Daisy </h2><p>Dunk the other end of your pin into the yellow nail polish (Kyeesâ personal fave is OPIâs Sunny Donât Tell A Sol, below). Place a dot in the center of each white circle you created. â[Make sure] to finish all the white dots and add the yellow at the end,â Kyees warns. Itâs best to leave a bit of drying time in-between: âThis prevents the yellow polish from bleeding into the white.â But hey, if that happens, you could always pivot to an equally fun <a class href="https://www.bustle.com/style/how-to-do-the-water-marble-nails-look-at-home">marble nail</a>.</p><div class="sCC iGR DDo"><div class="eFL bwf"><div class="SEh OHp"><div class="sCC Ffs vEZ"><div class><div class="iDB"><a class="Rya LAc" data-skimlink target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="https://www.target.com/p/opi-nail-lacquer-don-39-t-tell-a-sol-0-5-fl-oz/-/A-79929115?ref=tgt_adv_XS000000&amp;AFID=google_pla_df&amp;fndsrc=tgtao&amp;DFA=71700000012735304&amp;CPNG=PLA_Beauty%2BPersonal+Care%2BShopping_Local%7CBeauty_Ecomm_Beauty&amp;adgroup=SC_Health%2BBeauty&amp;LID=700000001170770pgs&amp;LNM=PRODUCT_GROUP&amp;network=g&amp;device=c&amp;location=9004351&amp;targetid=aud-804645065996:pla-897661776657&amp;ds_rl=1246978&amp;ds_rl=1248099&amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwwqaGBhBKEiwAMk-FtCjS1jgqch-omhlErxIGiockKBZn0JLCQK5ohKxUon97w9o42ydh-hoC2BUQAvD_BwE&amp;gclsrc=aw.ds"><div class="MQL Nut"><div class="yPq csi">OPI Nail Lacquer in Don't Tell A Sol</div><div class="OQa chk">Target</div></div><div class="ozJ qnK"><div class="vxZ wx_ IVX"><noscript><img src="https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/a9b5d514-4f9f-45ba-bc9a-2fe3be03ced6-guest_0dc2be20-b0e1-4110-b974-ecd6ff218349.webp?w=400&amp;h=286&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress" srcSet="https://imgix.bustle.com/uploads/image/2021/6/16/a9b5d514-4f9f-45ba-bc9a-2fe3be03ced6-guest_0dc2be20-b0e1-4110-b974-ecd6ff218349.webp?w=330&amp;h=236&amp;fit=crop&amp;cro